---
/**
 * The statement-block, in Verren's own voice — first person, signed by hand.
 * Pure typography, no imagery.
 */
---

<section id="introducing" class="py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="v-container md:border-t md:border-hairline md:pt-4">
    <div class="v-grid gap-y-4">
      <div class="col-span-4">
        <span class="v-chip reveal">Introducing Verren</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-4 md:col-span-6 md:col-start-5">
        <div class="max-w-[580px] space-y-[1em] text-h4 text-ink-body">
          <p class="reveal" data-reveal-delay="60">
            <strong>I'm Verren — a chief of staff for your practice.</strong> I connect
            to your email and calendar, work alongside the CRM you already run, and
            start doing the work — nothing to migrate, nothing to bet the practice on.
          </p>
          <p class="reveal" data-reveal-delay="140">
            <strong>I keep your book current so you don't have to.</strong> Every client
            profile updates itself — household changes, goals, concerns, commitments —
            and I tell you what matters before you'd otherwise find out.
          </p>
          <p class="reveal" data-reveal-delay="220">
            <strong>I handle the follow-through — with your approval.</strong> Anything
            I'm about to do, I show you first, in full. Nothing runs until you say go.
          </p>
          <p class="reveal" data-reveal-delay="300">
            <strong>You stay the advisor. I'll do everything else.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal mt-8" data-reveal-delay="360">
          <span class="hand-sign">— Verren</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .v-chip {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
  }
</style>
